# Cloudflare Pages 自定义响应头

# 默认：HTML 等页面不缓存，避免浏览器(含 bfcache/WebView)保留旧 HTML 而
# 引用到新部署已删除的哈希资源(JS/CSS)，导致整页丢失样式。
/*
  Cache-Control: no-store, must-revalidate

# 带内容哈希的静态资源(文件名随内容变化)可长期不可变缓存
/assets/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable
/hexagram/assets/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable
/astrology/assets/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable
/qimen/assets/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable
